chunks.html_content:
Use this service if you want to verify either a paper or electronic Apostille certificate issued in the UK.

You’ll need:

  • the date the Apostille was issued
  • the Apostille number
chunks.plain_content:
Verify an Apostille
Use this service if you want to verify either a paper or electronic Apostille certificate issued in the UK.
You’ll need:

  the date the Apostille was issued
  the Apostille number

chunks.html_content: The issue date and number are on the Apostille certificate.
chunks.plain_content:
